          "text": "**Frameworks analysis done.** Verdict: **none recommended as dependencies**. But the agent identified a concrete internal refactor that solves the same problem:\n\n> Replace 5 (soon 7) `show_*_popup` bools with a single `active_popup: Option<PopupKind>` enum. Dispatch on it first in `handle_key_event`. Eliminates the sequential `if show_X_popup` chain.\n\nThis is the right call — no framework dependency, ~40 lines of internal code, and it directly addresses the popup scaling problem for v0.5.\n\nStill waiting on the networking apps agent.",
